  "2026-04-26T13:26:59.897Z",cursor-agent,"Final audit evidence (2026-04-26 rerun): bootstrap passed with pm 2026.3.12, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.0, pnpm build, and npm install -g .; core dogfood harness /tmp/pm-full-audit-core-dEmZ9N passed 79/79 commands; calendar/extension harness /tmp/pm-full-audit-cal-ext-CCsKmu passed 32/32 unexpected checks with 3 expected validation failures documented; SDK smoke /tmp/pm-sdk-audit-pass-RaG8lS compiled and contracts had no missing core command names; remote telemetry stack had all 9 Docker Compose services running, public healthz HTTP 200, Grafana login reachable, synthetic UUID ingest persisted to Postgres, Loki/Tempo/Prometheus verified, DSAR export/delete worked, and opt-out/redaction behavior was verified locally. Fixes closed: pm-qgvj (.env ignore) and pm-k8i0 (strict create guidance). Open follow-up findings updated: pm-vhdc, pm-r9ei, pm-300m, pm-bqg4, pm-mpmv, pm-kglq, pm-jqgc. Final validation passed: pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all ok=true; dedupe parent_scope found 0 clusters; linked pm test run passed 4/4 including coverage 78 files/1052 tests and full test 78 files/1052 tests."
